{"tid":2088904,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"在南韓發傳單被約談 脫北者：這是首爾還是平壤？","createTime":"2020-07-01T11:50:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T23:32:04.000Z","uid":75656,"like":45,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"11ad5f966365588587d0240c2a3b9b3035f8f8d6","tid":2088904,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T11:50:55.000Z","msg":"《韓聯社》報導，脫北者團體「自由北韓運動聯盟」（Fighters for a Free North Korea）領導人朴尚學和「大泉」領導人朴正五今日上午到首爾市警察局接受約談。警方正在調查這對兄弟檔從事的活動是否違反《南北交流合作法》。<br />\n<br />\n在經過8個小時的調查後，出現在記者面前的朴尚學說，他「對這裡是平壤還是首爾感到困惑」，批評南韓政府「禁止言論自由...站在敵人那一方」。<br />\n<br />\n本月10日，南韓統一部以涉嫌違法為由，檢舉這2個脫北者團體，並取消其法人設立許可。上週，警方突襲搜索這2個團體的辦公室，將審查今日約談內容和搜獲的文件和裝置後，再決定是否採取進一步法律行動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3213728\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3213728&d=oa%2BbSijZO%2BDWYSsAyiffblKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=26f898d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3213728&h=989a2700\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3213728</a>"},{"pid":"6016d85e236eb138da202a733f20c42be09ef660","tid":2088904,"uid":124711,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T11:54:29.000Z","msg":"食屎啦文在寅"},{"pid":"56e061688585ec498d0c829094d3c64a483e4b04","tid":2088904,"uid":51701,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T11:55:21.000Z","msg":"文狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2b978c2422f8795abc4ecc723fe2a26b0172ab0","tid":2088904,"uid":51701,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T11:56:15.000Z","msg":"抵日本想踢你出聯盟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e82ab20286af9f9fdc720d41db9f0cc5818a3dfa","tid":2088904,"uid":27530,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T11:59:37.000Z","msg":"係咪姐係「民主建設北韓」、港版民建聯？"},{"pid":